{"tid":722611,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[升班冠聯之路]2017-18 LIHKG香港甲組女神聯賽升班附加賽四強次回合投選專區 #朱茵 游蕙禎 譚嘉儀 梁嘉琪","createTime":"2018-06-29T15:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T14:04:33.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"233725d1a85cad3178cb9527af4cfa9a5e4a7c46","tid":722611,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T15:59:37.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:00am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n朱茵v游蕙禎<br />\n譚嘉儀(模)v梁嘉琪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n甲組全季積分榜<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/umnriTu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FumnriTu.png&h=487bdb2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e43024c0bd7a905d857993a953d99d28cc7f62b","tid":722611,"uid":92376,"like":33,"dislike":37,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG香港甲組女神聯賽升班附加賽四強次回合</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-6-30 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/msJ5kSR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmsJ5kSR.png&h=2412694c&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/t8X8RMa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ft8X8RMa.png&h=66a3de83&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(6)朱茵vs游蕙禎(9)</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(首回合 23-45)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"a680ed98293f795fbd55913dc5875331f71e1af7","tid":722611,"uid":92376,"like":26,"dislike":41,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-6-30 12:02am-10:02pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jbnKAqT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjbnKAqT.png&h=ad3a151a&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/CdGYLFC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCdGYLFC.png&h=d43fcfa5&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(7)譚嘉儀(模)vs梁嘉琪(8)</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(首回合 40-34)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評評功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"6d4f9ecaf7bf42d0898dc5a798fc2fff829de8c5","tid":722611,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T16:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25978cc5f44b360b817428af224ab16c0ef40b9","tid":722611,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T16:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfccf25bbd0a2b2287452b3fd26e148